ZH: 这本书的作者是一位知名的小说家。
EN: The author of this book is a famous novelist.

ZH: 作者在书中描绘了一个令人印象深刻的角色。
EN: The author portrayed an impressive character in the book.

ZH: 读者们通常对作者的写作风格有自己独特的看法。
EN: Readers often have their own unique views on the author's writing style.

ZH: 作者的文章引起了广泛的讨论和争议。
EN: The author's article sparked widespread discussion and controversy.

ZH: 这篇散文无法知道作者的真实意图。
EN: It is impossible to discern the author's true intentions in this essay.

ZH: 作者用了许多隐喻和象征主题来表达他的观点。
EN: The author used many metaphors and symbolic themes to convey his views.

ZH: 读者们热切期待着作者的下一部作品。
EN: Readers eagerly anticipate the author's next work.

ZH: 这位作者以其深刻的见解而闻名。
EN: The author is renowned for his profound insights.

ZH: 作者的写作能力令人叹为观止。
EN: The author's writing prowess is truly remarkable.

ZH: 他是小说《时间机器》的作者。
EN: He is the author of the novel "The Time Machine".

ZH: 这本书的作者一直是我心目中的偶像。
EN: The author of this book has always been an idol in my heart.

ZH: 作者利用风趣幽默的语言吸引了许多读者。
EN: The author attracted many readers with his witty and humorous language.

ZH: 这部小说的成功在于作者的故事情节设置。
EN: The success of this novel lies in the author's plot development.

ZH: 作者的深情笔墨让读者很容易感同身受。
EN: The author's heartfelt writing makes it easy for readers to empathize.

ZH: 作者的作品深受学者们的推崇。
EN: The author's work is highly esteemed by scholars.

ZH: 作者的名字已经成为文学史上的一个传奇。
EN: The author's name has become a legend in literary history.

ZH: 读者们对作者的作品情有独钟。
EN: Readers have a special fondness for the author's works.

ZH: 这位作者是一位多产的作家，已出版十几本畅销书。
EN: The author is a prolific writer, having published over a dozen bestsellers.

ZH: 作者在小说中展现了生动的人物形象。
EN: The author brings vivid character images to life in the novel.

ZH: 作者的评论在文学界引起强烈反响。
EN: The author's critiques have sparked strong reactions in the literary world.
